msgid ""
"The same platform, running entirely inside your browser via WebAssembly. "
"Zero install, your data never leaves your machine. Try it at `datalab-"
"platform.com/web <https://datalab-platform.com/web/>`_ or browse the "
"`project on GitHub <https://github.com/DataLab-Platform/web>`__."
msgstr ""
"La même plateforme, s'exécutant entièrement dans votre navigateur via "
"WebAssembly. Aucune installation, vos données ne quittent jamais votre "
"machine. Essayez-la sur `datalab-platform.com/web <https://datalab-"
"platform.com/web/>`_ ou parcourez le `projet sur GitHub "
"<https://github.com/DataLab-Platform/web>`__."

